nodes.text: This purple-skinned being worked as an enforcer for Stenness Node-based crime lord Bogga the Hutt around 3999 BBY. He was part of a mission to Ambria in 3999 BBY, in an attempt to retrieve a lost shipment of Adegan crystals. This enforcer was the first to discover the crystals, but he was slain when Jedi apprentice Nomi Sunrider attacked his group.
